Package: whomapR
Title: Choropleth and bubble maps of the world and WHO regions, using the latest WHO geoJSON files
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: person("Takuya", "Yamanaka", email = "yamanakat@who.int", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0807-2370"))
Description: Loads WHO geoJSON files (2025) and provides a wrapper to ggplot2. Adapted from scripts of whomap package developed by Philippe Glaziou.
